<paragraph id="8BD7E2412E23FFA1FF0688B9FD34FC62" blockId="2.[166,1225,990,1849]" box="[219,696,990,1017]" pageId="2" pageNumber="183">
D e s c r i p t i o n (
<figureCitation id="1353FEC42E23FFA1FE4F88B9FE5DFC62" box="[402,465,990,1017]" captionStart="Fig" captionStartId="5.[174,207,1735,1757]" captionTargetBox="[230,1169,186,1697]" captionTargetId="figure-14@5.[220,1178,174,1703]" captionTargetPageId="5" captionText="Fig. 1. Acanthocephalan species from California sea lions (Zalophus californianus): A — Corynosoma strumosum, total view of adult male; B — Corynosoma obtuscens, total view of female; C — Profilicollis altmani, total view of immature male; D — Andracantha phalacrocoracis, anterior part of female; E — Andrcantha sp., total view of immature female. Scale bars: A, B, C, E — 1 mm, D — 500 μm." figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6454657" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/6454657/files/figure.png" pageId="2" pageNumber="183">figs 1</figureCitation>
, D; 
<figureCitation id="1353FEC42E23FFA1FDDC88B9FD9DFC62" box="[513,529,990,1017]" captionStart="Fig" captionStartId="7.[174,207,1642,1664]" captionTargetBox="[235,1128,177,1607]" captionTargetId="figure-14@7.[230,1175,142,1621]" captionTargetPageId="7" captionText="Fig. 2. Acanthocephalan species from California sea lions (Zalophus californianus): A — Andracantha sp., total view of immature male. Scale bar 1 mm; B — Andracantha sp., proboscis of female. Scale bar 500 μm; C — Andracantha sp., total view of immature female. Scale bar 1 mm; D — Andracantha phalacrocoracis, spines of ventral surface. Scale bar 1 mm; E — Corynosoma obtuscens, transitional hooks. Scale bar 50 μm; F — Corynosoma strumosum, transitional hooks. Scale bar 50 μm; G — Profilicollis altmani, longitudinal row of hooks. Scale bar 100 μm; H — Andracantha sp., posterior part of female. Scale bar 500 μm; J — Andracantha sp., longitudinal row of hooks.Scale bar 100 μm; K — Andracantha phalacrocoracis, longitudinal row of hooks. Scale bar 100 μm." figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6454661" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/6454661/files/figure.png" pageId="2" pageNumber="183">2</figureCitation>
, D, K; 
<tableCitation id="C6EAD7FA2E23FFA1FDBC88B9FD23FC62" box="[609,687,990,1017]" captionStart="Table 2" captionStartId="3.[165,232,505,527]" captionText="Table 2. Morphological features of Acanthocephala specimens found in California sea lions (Zalophus californianus). All measurements are in micrometers unless otherwise stated" pageId="2" pageNumber="183">table 2</tableCitation>
)
